title: Implant Attack
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

When a model with this biomorph inflicts an unsaved wound on a model while in close combat, it instead inflicts two unsaved wounds. This biomorph's effect comes into play //after// the opponent resolves any [[Feel No Pain]] rolls it may be entitled to.